# Trivy vulnerability ignore file
# Format: CVE-ID  # reason — reviewed by — date
#
# Add entries here ONLY after security review confirms the CVE is either:
#   a) a false positive
#   b) not exploitable in this deployment context
#   c) has no available fix and is accepted risk
#
# Example:
# CVE-2023-12345  # false positive in Alpine base image — no network exposure — reviewed 2025-01-01
